In [9]:
from wordcloud import WordCloud

wordcloud = WordCloud().generate(' '.join( \
    newsio['text_info']).replace("hong kong", "")\
    .replace("monday", "").replace("tuesday", "")\
    .replace("wednesday", "").replace("thursday", "")\
    .replace("friday", ""))

# Display the generated image:
plt.rcParams["figure.figsize"] = (10,6)
plt.imshow(wordcloud, interpolation='bilinear')
plt.axis("off")
plt.show()

In [28]:
ipo_data["Offer High"] = pd.to_numeric(ipo_data["Offer High"],errors='coerce')
ipo_data["Shares Offer"] = pd.to_numeric(\
    ipo_data["Shares Offer"],errors='coerce')

ipo_data["market_cap"] = ipo_data["Shares Offer"]\
* ipo_data["Offer High"]
ipo_data.groupby(["Listing Date"]).agg({"market_cap": "sum"})\
.reset_index().plot(x="Listing Date", y="market_cap", figsize=(10,6))
